short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Chrome Extension for emulating the Web2Native Bridge scheme

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Web2Native Bridge emulator is an extension which adds a new API to the "navigator" object.  This API allows ordinary web-pages launching and communicating with specifically crafted native applications currently limited to Java.

The extension depends on a native-mode proxy which does the actual dispatching.  All documentation and code is available at:
https://github.com/cyberphone/web2native-bridge
